{
  "stem": "19198.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- I do not recall any specifics.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- generally, it was the feeling of being completely isolated from the-- from the non-Jewish population, except for a few gutsy people who didn't mind the comments of their neighbors that they were still having contact with Jews.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Even they would-- and my grandparents' home, from-- through a back door that was not visible to the-- from the street.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The-- it was that-- that thorough and-- an exclusion from civic life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I-- I think it would be very difficult for anybody who has not gone through it to really imagine the-- the kind of feeling.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And even for me, it is difficult to describe because it-- there are so many intangibles that we take for granted.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the-- like, I can-- I can walk a street in my neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And even if I don't know the person, I can say, 'Good morning.' Well, there you-- you couldn't.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because, first of all, one did not say 'good morning' anymore in Germany.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You had to say, 'Heil Hitler.' And that I wouldn't say.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So just from one-- one kind of communication, you can imagine how thorough the exclusion was.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Within--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Within a very short time after they took over.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember how many weeks or months it was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They always were-- were visible because they-- everybody that was anybody was in uniform.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you-- you couldn't walk the street for five minutes without seeing somebody in some form of official clothing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if you-- if they were the party members or members of either the SR or the SS, they wore that kind of uniform.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If they were Hitler Youth or B-- Bund Deutscher Maedchen, or what it was called, you had that uniform.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
